author: Brian Johnson
title: Mixed report for housing
text:
Home / News / Construction & Development / Mixed report for housing A new report showed a monthly increase in permits for new multifamily construction, including this Portland Tower condominium tower under construction on the northwest corner of Eighth Street and Portland Avenue in Minneapolis. (Staff photo: Bill Klotz) Mixed report for housing By: Brian Johnson September 30, 2015 4:22 pm 0 The Twin Cities residential construction market had an uneven month in September, as multifamily housing activity advanced compared with year-ago levels, while single-family permits took a step back.
